These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, journalist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, february
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, mirinda
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the doctor and the journalist##2
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Job   | doctor     | bartender | journalist |
| Birthday   | february  | january    | april      |
| Beverage     | cola     | fanta      | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, chaman, pall-mall
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, balloon-flower
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, pilot, architect
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the architect is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the chaman-smoker is the architect##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is the pilot##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person who growsdaisy and the pall-mall-smoker##2
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar          | chaman  | aristoff     | pall-mall     |
| Flower   | daisy     | balloon-flower     | begonia      |
| Job   | architect  | pilot | dancer |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, fishing
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, cottage
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person driving the ship is between the cottage house and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person driving the ship is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby          | skydiving  | fishing     | drawing     |
| House           | cottage | ranch-style  | cape-cod   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Transport           | quad-bike     | ship | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, october
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, western, family
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, german, egyptian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the german##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person watching western movies and the japanese##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday    | december       | october  | july   |
| Movie-Genre     | western    | family  | fantasy |
| Nationality     | german   | egyptian | japanese        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, engineer
3 different games are played: domino, monopoly, poker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, may
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing poker and the engineer##2
3. the accountant is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Job         | accountant | dressmaker | engineer |
| Game   | poker  | monopoly       | domino       |
| Birthday           | july     | september       | may     |

