.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pumpkin
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, marigold
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, golf
House: colonial, townhouse, victorian
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person eating pineapple and the townhouse house##2
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Flower         | azalea | marigold      | balloon-flower |
| Sport   | water-polo   | cycling     | golf        |
| House           | colonial      | victorian       | townhouse      |

