.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, almond-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, turkish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, poppy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the colombian is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the colombian is between the turkish and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage          | almond-milk      | tea   | juice |
| Nationality         | australian | colombian | turkish |
| Flower   | azalea      | poppy | daffodil   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

