The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, june, february
1. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the person who likes turquise is between the russian and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Nationality         | russian    | february-climbing | japanese      |
| Color           | coral | turquise     | green |
| Birthday   | june     | february          | may       |

