House: cottage, gothic-revival, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, nigerian, russian
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is between the nigerian and the russian##2
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the nurse##1
6. the nurse is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Game      | snooker      | billiard | backgammon     |
| House          | gothic-revival   | cottage      | wooden     |
| Nationality   | russian  | indian      | nigerian |
| Job     | analyst | project-manager        | nurse     |

