The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person eating avocado is between the person eating grapes and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the french is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the thai is the person eating radish##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person driving the roller is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Flower       | daisy       | sunflower       | poppy    |
| Food         | radish | avocado | grapes |
| Nationality       | thai      | french         | turkish |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

