.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, lily
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, swisher, dannemann
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, golf, rugby
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | lily     | aconite | marigold      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Cigar   | dannemann   | swisher         | chaman     |
| Sport   | soccer | golf    | rugby     |

