There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the person playing go is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing go is between the person who growsmarigold and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
6. the person traveling to paris is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Game      | whist | go      | scrabble            |
| Flower           | begonia | daffodil | marigold |
| City   | san-francisco     | marseilles        | paris         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

