2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person watching time-travel movies and the oliveros-smoker##2
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
