.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, november
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, camping
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, subway
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is camping##2
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Birthday      | february    | november          | january |
| Hobby          | camping | video-games           | collecting        |
| Transport           | skateboard | subway | trike         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

