2. the colonial house is between the person traveling to london and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the person traveling to london and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
