.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, ebony, purple
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, librarian, journalist
City: miami, edinburgh, liverpool
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person traveling to miami and the owner of the horse##2
3. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is the person traveling to miami##1
5. the journalist is on the left of the person who likes black##1
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Color       | purple | black | ebony |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| Job       | journalist | lawyer   | librarian         |
| City   | liverpool    | edinburgh     | miami         |

