3. the british is the art-deco house##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the american is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
