.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, pepper, raspberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, cain, fonseca
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, indian
1. the egyptian is the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is between the person eating papaya and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the cain-smoker is the indian##1
5. the argentine is between the person eating pepper and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Food      | papaya | raspberry     | pepper        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Cigar   | cain        | alhambra       | fonseca      |
| Nationality           | indian           | argentine    | egyptian       |

