.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, indian, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, domino
1. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the indian is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the canadian is between the person playing domino and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar        | cain      | game | oliveros |
| Nationality         | indian     | canadian    | russian        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Game   | bridge          | backgammon     | domino       |

 